Settings for Cygwin, using the GNU gfortran.

ESMF requires gfortran 4.3 or later.

Requires the following environment settings:

ESMF_COMPILER gfortran

Note that if the gfortran-4 and g++-4 packages have been
installed via the cygwin setup installer, the ESMF compiler
defaults need to be overridden by setting environment 
variables:

ESMF_F90 gfortran-4
ESMF_CXX g++-4

Alternatively the ESMF_F90DEFAULT and ESMF_CXXDEFAULT compiler
names used in build_rules.mk can be changed to:

ESMF_F90DEFAULT    = gfortran-4
ESMF_CXXDEFAULT    = g++-4

